<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1436,1911,2015]" lastBlockId="10.[151,1436,152,448]" lastPageId="10" lastPageNumber="53" pageId="9" pageNumber="52">
Pygofer (
<figureCitation box="[305,392,1911,1937]" captionStart="FIGURES 28–35" captionStartId="9.[151,270,1732,1756]" captionTargetBox="[168,1419,204,1681]" captionTargetId="figure-124@9.[151,1436,194,1708]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIGURES 28–35. Exogonia luteovittata sp. nov.: (28) body of female paratype, lateral view; (29) head, pronotum, and mesonotum of male paratype, dorsal view; (30–35) male holotype: (30) pygofer, lateral view; (31) subgenital plate, ventral view; (32) connective and style, dorsal view; (33) aedeagus and basal portion of gonoduct, lateral view; (34) paraphyses, lateral view; (35) paraphyses, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5321366" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5321366/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="52">Fig. 30</figureCitation>
), in lateral view, with macrosetae on apical portion and extending anteriorly along ventral margin; apical portion with small, ventral inner process bearing numerous setae. Subgenital plates (
<figureCitation box="[1306,1392,1950,1976]" captionStart="FIGURES 28–35" captionStartId="9.[151,270,1732,1756]" captionTargetBox="[168,1419,204,1681]" captionTargetId="figure-124@9.[151,1436,194,1708]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIGURES 28–35. Exogonia luteovittata sp. nov.: (28) body of female paratype, lateral view; (29) head, pronotum, and mesonotum of male paratype, dorsal view; (30–35) male holotype: (30) pygofer, lateral view; (31) subgenital plate, ventral view; (32) connective and style, dorsal view; (33) aedeagus and basal portion of gonoduct, lateral view; (34) paraphyses, lateral view; (35) paraphyses, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5321366" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5321366/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="52">Fig. 31</figureCitation>
), in ventral view, gradually tapered toward apex; with macrosetae near outer margin. Styles (
<figureCitation box="[1219,1309,1989,2015]" captionStart="FIGURES 28–35" captionStartId="9.[151,270,1732,1756]" captionTargetBox="[168,1419,204,1681]" captionTargetId="figure-124@9.[151,1436,194,1708]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIGURES 28–35. Exogonia luteovittata sp. nov.: (28) body of female paratype, lateral view; (29) head, pronotum, and mesonotum of male paratype, dorsal view; (30–35) male holotype: (30) pygofer, lateral view; (31) subgenital plate, ventral view; (32) connective and style, dorsal view; (33) aedeagus and basal portion of gonoduct, lateral view; (34) paraphyses, lateral view; (35) paraphyses, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5321366" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5321366/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="52">Fig. 32</figureCitation>
), in dorsal view, short, extending approximately as far posteriorly as apex of connective; with distinct external median lobe; apical portion beyond lobe curved, with few setae; apex expanded, truncate. Connective (
<figureCitation box="[1300,1390,190,216]" captionStart="FIGURES 28–35" captionStartId="9.[151,270,1732,1756]" captionTargetBox="[168,1419,204,1681]" captionTargetId="figure-124@9.[151,1436,194,1708]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIGURES 28–35. Exogonia luteovittata sp. nov.: (28) body of female paratype, lateral view; (29) head, pronotum, and mesonotum of male paratype, dorsal view; (30–35) male holotype: (30) pygofer, lateral view; (31) subgenital plate, ventral view; (32) connective and style, dorsal view; (33) aedeagus and basal portion of gonoduct, lateral view; (34) paraphyses, lateral view; (35) paraphyses, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5321366" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5321366/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="53">Fig. 32</figureCitation>
), in dorsal view, Y-shaped. Aedeagus (
<figureCitation box="[557,643,229,255]" captionStart="FIGURES 28–35" captionStartId="9.[151,270,1732,1756]" captionTargetBox="[168,1419,204,1681]" captionTargetId="figure-124@9.[151,1436,194,1708]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIGURES 28–35. Exogonia luteovittata sp. nov.: (28) body of female paratype, lateral view; (29) head, pronotum, and mesonotum of male paratype, dorsal view; (30–35) male holotype: (30) pygofer, lateral view; (31) subgenital plate, ventral view; (32) connective and style, dorsal view; (33) aedeagus and basal portion of gonoduct, lateral view; (34) paraphyses, lateral view; (35) paraphyses, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5321366" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5321366/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="53">Fig. 33</figureCitation>
) short; shaft, in lateral view, slightly curved ventrally, with distinct dorsoapical expanded lobe; in dorsal view, with pair of lateral spiniform projections on median portion. Paraphyses (
<figureCitation box="[298,430,306,332]" captionStart="FIGURES 28–35" captionStartId="9.[151,270,1732,1756]" captionTargetBox="[168,1419,204,1681]" captionTargetId="figure-124@9.[151,1436,194,1708]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIGURES 28–35. Exogonia luteovittata sp. nov.: (28) body of female paratype, lateral view; (29) head, pronotum, and mesonotum of male paratype, dorsal view; (30–35) male holotype: (30) pygofer, lateral view; (31) subgenital plate, ventral view; (32) connective and style, dorsal view; (33) aedeagus and basal portion of gonoduct, lateral view; (34) paraphyses, lateral view; (35) paraphyses, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5321366" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5321366/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="53">Figs 34, 35</figureCitation>
) with anterior pair of rami, in lateral view, elongate, directed anterodorsally; posterior pair, in lateral view, directed dorsally, apical portion curved posteroventrally; stalk approximately as long as rami. Anal tube (segment X), in lateral view, with pair of small processes on ventroapical margin, similar to those of pygofer.
</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5321370" ID-Zenodo-Dep="5321370" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5321370/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="53" startId="10.[151,270,1450,1474]" targetBox="[160,1421,515,1399]" targetPageId="10">
